{"id": 3080, "genre": 1001, "title": "你心目中比较理想的亲密关系状态是啥样的？", "description": "作为一个当代人，你对亲密关系都有哪些不一样的理解（或者说预期）？（题图来自：视觉中国 ©️ Corbis RM）", "record_count": 1619, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201912050111499xSoNbs4FtUnueOW.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-12-04T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 350208, "content": "同你说话，像跟自己说话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066159}, {"id": 350209, "content": "三观一致，你不找我，我不找你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673915}, {"id": 350212, "content": "如图", "image": "img/option/option/201912091353264j1MShxLQzXUk2Vw.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497222}, {"id": 350218, "content": "encourage each other to become a better self, brave what we fear.", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465760}, {"id": 350219, "content": "Bakshdkekxihxkemkszhsjsndnxndmsmnsbdhsnenejwndbdbjddbbkwbsghsbekxndmajsggsusbshxbrkddnsjdhdurhbekdndbdbsjsmavahjabdjdkfnrbrusjdbekdkenegsbsj", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465760}, {"id": 350221, "content": "长长短短，\n断断续续。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1465760}, {"id": 350230, "content": "当对方需要交流能够倾听反馈，分享生活。能够转身发现就在身后，或许脚步不一致，但距离总是保持得恰到好处。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310603}, {"id": 351269, "content": "白天有各自为之奋斗的事业 夜晚有一起聊不完的话题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1480373}, {"id": 350766, "content": "安心，舒服，温暖，不患得患失", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674815}, {"id": 350260, "content": "先听你的，不过你要听我的～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1284224}, {"id": 351545, "content": "互相联系且互相独立", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666326}, {"id": 350779, "content": "看到这人就觉得特高兴，特想说话，这人看到我也是一样的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 350013, "content": "像综艺里调侃的那样，俩人住隔壁，一起吃饭聊天，但是“请别跟我住一起”", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 350269, "content": "晚上吃麻辣锅/给我留两块薯饼/往东400米再左拐...有人懂我意思吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674164}, {"id": 352573, "content": "支持尊重成长不放开手", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315624}, {"id": 350014, "content": "不需要跟对方报备最近跟谁吃了饭/见了面，当然了，愿意主动聊聊也不错", "image": null, "praise_count": 47, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 350015, "content": "有起码的默契（比如一起玩梗这种），有至少一个共同爱好", "image": null, "praise_count": 178, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 350016, "content": "吵架并不可怕，但是不要冷战或者说“你别管”之类的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 350018, "content": "“在一起”并不比“分手”优越，如果谈不来分开是好事", "image": null, "praise_count": 81, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 350019, "content": "相互尊重，留有空间。关心彼此，能进行有效沟通。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977996}, {"id": 350020, "content": "睡在上下铺的兄弟…", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 978960}, {"id": 350021, "content": "互相有需要的时候可以随时在一起，想自己做点事的时候可以单独专注在自己的世界里", "image": null, "praise_count": 132, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355256}, {"id": 350023, "content": "互相尊重，永远不拒绝沟通。平时既有共同的时间，也有独处的时间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 455, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 685031}, {"id": 350024, "content": "彼此称对方为哥和姐。给对方起个不难听的外号。分享彼此快乐，都成为更好的人。一起做爱做的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1643494}, {"id": 350025, "content": "即使是想吃独食也可以大方地告诉ta，不用假装热情分ta一份", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673516}, {"id": 350026, "content": "“分开时各自安逸，在一起天下无敌” ，忘了谁说的了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1259801}, {"id": 350027, "content": "平等，自由，开放", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1588809}, {"id": 350028, "content": "你是你，我是我，我们是我们", "image": null, "praise_count": 202, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1374965}, {"id": 350029, "content": "相互理解尊重，能够进行很好的沟通，理性包容。有时间和距离不会冲淡的感情", "image": null, "praise_count": 87, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1672508}, {"id": 352334, "content": "善解人意", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1680555}, {"id": 350031, "content": "我们彼此的世界可以有交集，但是终归是属于各自的世界，可以交流，却互不干涉", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1664029}, {"id": 350032, "content": "尊重，彼此坦诚，没有顾忌地表达感情，好聚好散。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1560782}, {"id": 350034, "content": "我的事情你都知道，你的事情我都知道，这样子的安全感么", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352903}, {"id": 350035, "content": "不用刻意去找话题，就算没话说也不会尴尬。", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1188058}, {"id": 350037, "content": "可以我在葬礼上描述我一生的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 46, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 651972}, {"id": 350038, "content": "她和我都有自己的生活，我们会在闲暇的时间相互陪伴，享受生活，并且成为对方的依靠。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673388}, {"id": 350039, "content": "有事就说，不要总是说“没事”“没关系”“不用”", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648526}, {"id": 350040, "content": "举案齐眉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924661}, {"id": 350041, "content": "懂得自我。关心彼此。永远陪伴。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 948915}, {"id": 350042, "content": "亲密关系对我来是一种我一辈子不会拥有的能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666203}, {"id": 350043, "content": "永远也说不完的话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484388}, {"id": 350044, "content": "互相尊重和包容，遇见事情可以共同面对，能有一定的默契，接纳彼此的生命。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673563}, {"id": 350045, "content": "只要互看一眼，便能知道你的所有沉默下的千言万语。", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1200442}, {"id": 350047, "content": "默契！观点相同、有着共同的爱好，能成为知心的人！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1673572}, {"id": 350048, "content": "不会依赖对方。因为离开不习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1480389}, {"id": 350050, "content": "基于顺畅地平等沟通，一起携手成长，探索未知", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 171698}, {"id": 350051, "content": "我是爱你的，你是自由的", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 565141}, {"id": 350053, "content": "我爱你，但是我不会100%附和你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493266}, {"id": 350054, "content": "和藹可親，有更多的共同點與愛好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1555161}, {"id": 350566, "content": "知音～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674636}]}